17844179,-0.01477462,0.0510888,0.02516712,0.07079394,0.03656361,0.05586034,0.03428598,0.08029969,-0.02349888,0.03800937,-0.02673058,-0.01771472,-0.03666652,0.01904199,0.00934659,0.0323095,-0.02058616,-0.00374774,-0.0204126,0.07969954,-0.00376367,0.17459606,-0.10859301,-0.04195903,-0.06024462,0.01915902,-0.02972368,-0.04383178,-0.03085126,-0.04537614,0.01735473,-0.00444815,0.0774327,-0.00316912,0.01544127,0.02247068,-0.03030597,0.01487192,-0.03753105,0.05219426,0.0217324,0.00181652],"last_embed":{"hash":"9p8x85","tokens":459}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"9p8x85","at":1772114034093},"key":"_007.Books/_007.Books.md#_007.Books#{2}","lines":[14,87],"size":6073,"outlinks":[{"title":"_007.Books","target":"_007.Books","line":1},{"title":"📘Discourses","target":"📘Discourses","line":2},{"title":"📘The Bed of Procrustes","target":"📘The Bed of Procrustes","line":3},{"title":"12 Rules For Life","target":"12 Rules For Life","line":4},{"title":"Art of War","target":"Art of War","line":5},{"title":"Atomic Habits","target":"Atomic Habits","line":6},{"title":"Blue Like Jazz📕","target":"Blue Like Jazz📕","line":8},{"title":"Nobody will listen to you unless they sense that you like them.","target":"Nobody will listen to you unless they sense that you like them.","line":9},{"title":"Analyze the mission.","target":"Analyze the mission.","line":11},{"title":"Cover and Move means teamwork. All elements within the greater team are crucial and must work together to accomplish the mission, mutually supporting one another for that singular purpose.","target":"Cover and Move means teamwork. All elements within the greater team are crucial and must work together to accomplish the mission, mutually supporting one another for that singular purpose.","line":12},{"title":"Don’t ask your leader what you should do, tell them what you are going to do.","target":"Don’t ask your leader what you should do, tell them what you are going to do.","line":13},{"title":"Everyone that is part of the mission must know and understand his or her role in the mission and what to do in the event of likely contingencies.","target":"Everyone that is part of the mission must know and understand his or her role in the mission and what to do in the event of likely contingencies.","line":14},{"title":"Extreme Ownership 📕","target":"Extreme Ownership 📕","line":15},{"title":"If substandard performance is accepted and no one is held accountable—if there are no consequences—that poor performance becomes the new standard. Therefore, leaders must enforce standards.","target":"If substandard performance is accepted and no one is held accountable—if there are no consequences—that poor performance becomes the new standard. Therefore, leaders must enforce standards.","line":16},{"title":"Leaders must be free to move to where they are most needed","target":"Leaders must be free to move to where they are most needed","line":17},{"title":"Not knowing the **why** prohibits you from believing in the mission. When you are in a leadership position, that is a recipe for failure, and it is unacceptable. As a leader, you must believe.”","target":"Not knowing the **why** prohibits you from believing in the mission. When you are in a leadership position, that is a recipe for failure, and it is unacceptable. As a leader, you must believe.”","line":18},{"title":"Simplifying as much as possible is crucial to success.","target":"Simplifying as much as possible is crucial to success.","line":19},{"title":"Take responsibility for leading everyone in your world, subordinates and superiors alike.  If someone isn’t doing what you want or need them to do, look in the mirror first and determine what you can do to better enable this.","target":"Take responsibility for leading everyone in your world, subordinates and superiors alike.  If someone isn’t doing what you want or need them to do, look in the mirror first and determine what you can do to better enable this.","line":20},{"title":"The moment the alarm goes off is the first test; it sets the tone for the rest of the day. The test is not a complex one when the alarm goes off, do you get up out of bed, or do you lie there in comfort and fall back to sleep?","target":"The moment the alarm goes off is the first test; it sets the tone for the rest of the day. The test is not a complex one when the alarm goes off, do you get up out of bed, or do you lie there in comfort and fall back to sleep?","line":21},{"title":"When overwhelmed, fall back upon this principle Prioritize and Execute.","target":"When overwhelmed, fall back upon this principle Prioritize and Execute.","line":22},{"title":"Good to Great","target":"Good to Great","line":23},{"title":"How To Win Friends and Influence People","target":"How To Win Friends and Influence People","line":24},{"title":"Mans Search for Meaning 📕","target":"Mans Search for Meaning 📕","line":25},{"title":"Meditations","target":"Meditations","line":26},{"title":"Never Split  the Difference 📕","target":"Never Split  the Difference 📕","line":27},{"title":"Principles by Ray Dalio","target":"Principles by Ray Dalio","line":28},{"title":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","target":"“Couples don’t fall out of love so much as they fall out of repentance.”","line":30},{"title":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","target":"“GETTING TO KNOW YOUR SPOUSE” QUESTIONNAIRE","line":31},{"title":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","target":"“What if God designed marriage to make us holy more than to make us happy”25 (Location 870)","line":32},{"title":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","target":"4 Horseman of broken marriage - Criticism, Contempt, Defensiveness, Stonewalling","line":33},{"title":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","target":"A wife flourishes with a loving husband, and a husband becomes courageous with a respectful wife.","line":34},{"title":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","target":"Action before feeling - Action promotes feelings","line":35},{"title":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","target":"Being the responsible head does not mean that a man does everything in the family, but rather that everything gets done.","line":36},{"title":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","target":"Couples who pray and play together stay together.","line":37},{"title":"Create habits of doing things together","target":"Create habits of doing things together","line":38},{"title":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","target":"Disagreement - first agree you are both on the same team and work towards same goal. Choice either to drift apart or get closer to each other.","line":39},{"title":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","target":"Everyone has something to teach you if you are humble enough to learn.","line":40},{"title":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","target":"Everything, for a man, is viewed as respect or disrespect. For a woman, everything is seen as loving or unloving.","line":41},{"title":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","target":"Fruitfulness of Wife and Husban serving God together.","line":42},{"title":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","target":"If we do not choose humility, God will choose humiliation for us. So we must willfully, earnestly, and continually humble ourselves.","line":43},{"title":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","target":"Importance of being emotionally avalible for your wife. Avoid the problem solving mode. She doesnt need to be \"figured out\".","line":44},{"title":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","target":"It takes between nine and fourteen years for a couple to become not entirely unselfish, but rather less selfish, and begin to shift from “me” to “we.”","line":45},{"title":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","target":"Love is more like a song than a math equation. It requires a sense of poetry and passion to be any good at it.","line":46},{"title":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","target":"Marriage either gets bitter or gets better.","line":47},{"title":"Marriage is about friendship.","target":"Marriage is about friendship.","line":48},{"title":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","target":"Martin Luther King and His wife Katie","line":49},{"title":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","target":"Our family television is also in the most visible area of the home in an effort to help us monitor what our children watch.","line":50},{"title":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","target":"Our marriages only seem “unfixable” if we are unwilling to repent.","line":51},{"title":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","target":"Our value comes not from what we do; rather, what we do comes from our value as God’s image bearers. (Location 1669)","line":52},{"title":"Planning in family","target":"Planning in family","line":53},{"title":"Real Marriage 📕","target":"Real Marriage 📕","line":54},{"title":"Sex","target":"Sex","line":55},{"title":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","target":"The only alternative to forgiveness is bitterness. And the only alternative to bitterness is forgiveness.","line":56},{"title":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","target":"When we are sinned against, we need to forgive quickly.","line":57},{"title":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","target":"Your spouse is the most sanctifying, and often most frustrating, relationship you will have.","line":58},{"title":"Saving Your Marriage Before It Starts 📕","target":"Saving Your Marriage Before It Starts 📕","line":59},{"title":"God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","target":"God doesn’t give us crying, pooping children because he wants to advance our careers. He gives them to us to create chaos and deter us from investing too much energy in the gluttonous idols of self-absorption.","line":61},{"title":"Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.","target":"Life does seem like a game of poker. There’s all this acceptance and power and love in the middle, and we’re all holding our cards close to our chest trying to win it. It feels like the dumbest thing to do would be to show our cards.","line":62},{"title":"Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","target":"Loving a Woman is scarier than climbing a mountain or sailing an ocean. Dead or alive, you’re still a man. A woman, though, can rob your manhood and reduce you to a boy at the drop of a word. It’s no wonder we all try to control each other.","line":63},{"title":"Scary Close 📕","target":"Scary Close 📕","line":64},{"title":"The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.","target":"The reality is people are impressed with all kinds of things - intelligence, power, money, charm, talent, and so on. But the ones we tend to stay in love with are, in the long run, the ones who do a decent job loving us back.","line":65},{"title":"We will never feel loved until we drop the act, until we’re willing to show our true selves to the people around us.","target":"We will never feel loved until we drop the act, until we’re willing to show our true selves to the people around us.","line":66},{"title":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","target":"When you are conquering world you are rewarded for staying in control. You have to let go in order to gain intimacy.","line":67},{"title":"The Five Elements of Effective Thinking","target":"The Five Elements of Effective Thinking","line":68},{"title":"The Meaning of Marriage 📕","target":"The Meaning of Marriage 📕","line":69},{"title":"The Pleasure of Finding Things Out","target":"The Pleasure of Finding Things Out","line":70},{"title":"Things I Wish I'd Known Before We Got Married 📕","target":"Things I Wish I'd Known Before We Got Married 📕","line":71},{"title":"Think Like a Freak 📕","target":"Think Like a Freak 📕","line":72},{"title":"Wild at Heart","target":"Wild at Heart","line":73}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"9p8x85","at":1772114034093}},
